OL,3,CUniversity closures may become
OL,4,C'common' if funding is not improved
OL,5,Cfor sector
OL,7,FUniversity closures could "become
OL,8,Fcommon" if funding is not improved for
OL,9,Fthe higher education sector, a former
OL,10,Fvice chancellor has warned.
OL,12,FThe budgets of English universities
OL,13,Fare under "intense pressure" and
OL,14,F"painful choices" are already being
OL,15,Fmade, according to a report published
OL,16,Fby the Higher Education Policy
OL,17,FInstitute (Hepi) think tank.
