OL,5,Cfor sector
OL,7,FThe report ` authored by Professor Sir
OL,8,FChris Husbands, former vice-chancellor
OL,9,Fat Sheffield Hallam University `
OL,10,Fhighlights the challenges facing
OL,11,Funiversities as a result of frozen
OL,12,Ftuition fees for home students, visa
OL,13,Frestrictions on international students
OL,14,Fand "structural flaws" in research
OL,15,Ffunding.
