OL,7,FIn the paper, published ahead of the
OL,8,FGeneral Election, Sir Chris, who
OL,9,Fstepped down as vice chancellor of
OL,10,FSheffield Hallam in December, sets out
OL,11,Ffour possible scenarios for the future
OL,12,Fof English higher education and looks
OL,13,Fat what they could mean for students
OL,14,Fand universities.
OL,16,FIn the first scenario ` which
OL,17,Fconsiders what happens on the current
OL,18,Ffunding trajectory ` Sir Chris warns
OL,19,Fthat "university retrenchment,
OL,20,Finstitutional mergers and failures
OL,21,Fbecome common".
OL,26,@{D@FOU}D@NO]
