OL,5,Cfor sector
OL,7,FIf the next government does not make
OL,8,Fundergraduate tuition or maintenance
OL,9,Ffunding better, does not tackle flaws
OL,10,Fin research funding, and visa
OL,11,Frestrictions on international students
OL,12,Fremain then the number of institutions
OL,13,Fcould fall and the sector may become
OL,14,F"adept" in managing market exits, the
OL,15,Freport said.
