OL,7,FThe report, sponsored by the Policy
OL,8,FInstitute at King's College London
OL,9,F(KCL), suggests that an alternative
OL,10,Fscenario ` where the sector is fully
OL,11,Ffunded for high participation,
OL,12,Fresearch and innovation ` would allow
OL,13,Finstitutions to plan long-term
OL,14,Finvestments in their communities and
OL,15,Fregions.
