OL,7,FIn the paper, Sir Chris said:
OL,8,F"Scenarios 1 and 2 are, of course,
OL,9,Fextremes. Scenario 1 paints a picture
OL,10,Fof the higher education sector in
OL,11,FEngland if government does not
OL,12,Fconfront policy choices for
OL,13,Funiversities and sees the sector
OL,14,Fspending the next decade responding to
OL,15,Fthe consequences.
