OL,5,Cfor sector
OL,7,F"Scenario 2 paints a picture of a
OL,8,Ffinancially secure sector. If it
OL,9,Fappears politically and economically
OL,10,Funlikely, it is not too far from the
OL,11,Fpolicy positions of the main sector
OL,12,Frepresentative bodies looking for
OL,13,Fsustainable student fees, investment
OL,14,Fin the full costs of research and
OL,15,Fflexibilities in the international
OL,16,Fstudent market."
