OL,7,FHe added: "The shape of higher
OL,8,Feducation in 2024 is a consequence of
OL,9,Fprevious interactions between
OL,10,Funiversities and policy. It could `
OL,11,Fand will ` change.
OL,13,F"Whoever wins the election on July 4
OL,14,Fwill need to think hard about the
OL,15,Fhigher education the country needs and
OL,16,Fis willing to support."
