OL,7,FIn a foreword to the report, Professor
OL,8,FShitij Kapur, vice-chancellor and
OL,9,Fpresident of KCL, said the "funding
OL,10,Fcrisis" facing the higher education
OL,11,Fsector needs urgent attention by the
OL,12,Fnext government.
OL,14,FHe said: "UK universities are held in
OL,15,Fhigh esteem all over the world `
OL,16,Fenvied for their excellence and widely
OL,17,Femulated.
